speaker.name: Laysa Uchoa
speaker.biography: Laysa is a developer working towards a more diverse and fun Python community by organizing Pyladies Munich Chapter. Her passion for sharing knowledge and OSS has led her to work as developer advocate for Aiven. She help users understand databases and do cool things with them. Besides Python, she like cyberpunk movies, tea, and human languages.
